      "content_markdown": "# Vowel Marks — Part 1\n\nLearn how vowel marks change the inherent 'a' of consonants.\n\n### Today's Characters\n**ಕಾ** · **ಕಿ** · **ಕೀ** · **ಕು** · **ಕೂ**"
    },
    {
      "type": "content",
      "step_title": "Learn: ಕಾ (kaa)",
      "content_markdown": "## ಕಾ — kaa\n\n**Sound:** kaa as in 'calm'.\n\n**Visual:** Adds a stroke to the right of the consonant."
