      "feedback": "Correct! **ಕಾ** is the 'kaa' sound."
    },
    {
      "type": "content",
      "step_title": "Learn: ಕಿ (ki)",
      "content_markdown": "## ಕಿ — ki\n\n**Sound:** ki as in 'kit'.\n\n**Visual:** Adds a small hook/mark on top."
